title: Commander Keen - the band!
content:
Earlier this year I saw adverts around the city for a local band called "Commandar Keen" and thought it was funny how the word "Mandark" was in their name. They play in bars, so they're probably just yet another NZ guitars+drums+yell band.

Well, I've since found more adverts of theirs around the place, and they spell their name "Commander Keen" now, and also demonstrated more of their copyright-infringing originality but representing themselves in the style of South Park characters. Hehe.

I haven't bothered going to hear them though.----------
